OL,3,CFootage captures attempted 'petrol
OL,4,Cbomb' attack
OL,6,FA masked man caught on doorbell
OL,7,Ffootage throwing what was reported to
OL,8,Fbe a 'petrol bomb' at a woman's home
OL,9,Fin Carlisle has been jailed for four
OL,10,Fyears.
OL,12,FJames Heaney, 27, had left the
OL,13,Fdaughter of his victim a voicemail
OL,14,Fmessage ordering her to contact him
OL,15,Fwithin two hours or her home would "go
OL,16,Fup in flames", before attempting the
OL,17,Fpetrol bomb attack on June 18.
