OL,6,FThe victim had returned to her Well
OL,7,FBank Place property in Denton Holme at
OL,8,Faround 7pm, just minutes before the
OL,9,F"chilling" attempted arson attack,
OL,10,FCarlisle crown court heard.
OL,12,FHer doorbell video camera captured the
OL,13,Fmoment James Ross Heaney, masked by a
OL,14,Fscarf and hood, appeared to light a
OL,15,Fbottle he was carrying before throwing
OL,16,Fit towards the building. It smashed
OL,17,Fagainst a wall but little damage was
OL,18,Factually caused.
