OL,6,FA neighbour tried to chase Heaney, of
OL,7,FNewlaithes Avenue, Carlisle, as he
OL,8,Ffled the scene. Minutes later he was
OL,9,Farrested outside his home.
OL,11,FThe court heard how, before the
OL,12,Foffence, the woman had received a
OL,13,Fphone call in which Heaney made
OL,14,Freference to being "around the corner".
OL,16,F"Two hours - and I'm being generous -
OL,17,For your house goes up in flames," he
OL,18,Fhad stated.
