OL,6,F"Thankfully there was no fire that
OL,7,Ftook light," the judge told Heaney.
OL,8,F"But the outcome of this could have
OL,9,Fbeen very, very different. It was
OL,10,Fplainly serious and terrifying for the
OL,11,Fhouseholder."
OL,13,FConcluding Heaney was a dangerous
OL,14,Foffender, the judge ordered him to
OL,15,Fserve an extended three-year licence
OL,16,Fperiod.
